    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Raid to Recover Supplies",
    "TitleKey": "CFP_RetrieveCargo_CrimBase_H_title_001",
    "Description": "Hey,\n\nOutlaws in the system have been getting aggressive lately, targeting more of our convoys. They recently ambushed one of our cargo ships and stole supplies desperately needed by our operations. If we don\u2019t get it back, we\u2019re worried that the locals will start losing faith. They need to know that Citizens for Prosperity can\u2019t just be bullied out of operation.\n\nWe managed to track the outlaws to ~mission(Location|Address). Now we need someone who isn\u2019t afraid of crossing these criminals to recover the shipment and deliver it to ~mission(Destination|Address). \n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n\nSo, do you think you could make the run for us?\n\nThanks,\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
    "DescriptionKey": "CFP_RetrieveCargo_CrimBase_H_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hey,\n\nOutlaws in the system have been getting aggressive lately, targeting more of our convoys. They recently ambushed one of our cargo ships and stole supplies desperately needed by our operations. If we don\u2019t get it back, we\u2019re worried that the locals will start losing faith. They need to know that Citizens for Prosperity can\u2019t just be bullied out of operation.\n\nWe managed to track the outlaws to [Location|Address]. Now we need someone who isn\u2019t afraid of crossing these criminals to recover the shipment and deliver it to [Destination|Address]. \n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n\nSo, do you think you could make the run for us?\n\nThanks,\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
